title: Tribute to David Lynch
description:
Inspired by my time at WCBN 88.3 FM Ann Arbor, this is a mix of themes / songs / tunes / dialogue from David Lynch's films from ERASERHEAD to MULHOLLAND DRIVE.

Im Abendrot Gewandhausorchester Leipzig, Kurt Masur
Slaughterhouse Powermad, Tim Bomba
Wicked Game Chris Isaak, Erik Jacobsen
I'm Bill Eraserhead Soundtrack
Blue Velvet Bobby Vinton
Elephant Man John Morris
In Heaven The Lady in the Radiator
There's Sometime A Buggy The Cowboy
Love Letters Straight From My Heart Kitty Lester
In Dreams Roy Orbison
Llorando (Crying) Rebekah Del Rio
I'm Deranged David Bowie
Perfect Drug Nine Inch Nails
Moving Through Time Angelo Badalamenti
Pink Room Angelo Badalamenti
Sycamore Trees Little Jimmy Scott
Falling Julee Cruise
I've Told Every Little Star Linda Scott
Dune - Main Theme Toto, Brian Eno
Rammstein Rammstein
Hierate Mich Rammstein
This Magic Moment Lou Reed
Give Me Back My Phone Mystery Man
Be Bop A Lula Gene Vincent, The Blue Caps
16 Reasons (Why I Love You) Connie Stevens
Baby, Please Don't Go Them
